# DO NOT ADD SUPABASE CONFIGURATION HERE
# ==========================================
# Supabase is NOT used in ANY configuration
# The application is 100% dependent on the custom external API (helixgeneralhardware.com/api.php)
# All database operations go through src/integrations/database/external-api-adapter.ts
